        <obo:IAO_0000115>A coast is the area where land meets the sea, ocean, or lake.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <rdfs:comment>Used for both marine and lake coasts. The boundary of the coast is fuzzy and it overlaps both the water body and land in quesiton. Compared to &apos;shore&apos;</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">coast</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
