        <obo:IAO_0000115>An environment which is determined by materials which bear significant concentrations of salts.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000118>Saline</obo:IAO_0000118>
        <oboInOwl:inSubset>envoEmpo</oboInOwl:inSubset>
        <rdfs:comment>The thresholds for &quot;significant&quot; concentrations of salts vary widely and thus no committment is made in this class. Subclasses with more explicit thresholds can be made upon request.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">saline environment</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
