        <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ENVO_02500027"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A process during which an ecosystem - natural or anthropised - is changed by the actions of humans.</obo:IAO_0000115>
