        <obo:IAO_0000115>A process which diminishes the functioning of an ecosystem located on land.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000116>An SDGIO request. Likely to be refined and revised.</obo:IAO_0000116>
        <rdfs:comment>This could include, for example, reducing soil health, pollinator activity, or an ecosystem&apos;s ability  to sequester carbon.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>land degradation</rdfs:label>
    </owl:Class>
    <owl:Axiom>
